title: Ajay Pal
text: I am a Biotechnologist by training, Fascinated by Neurodevelopmental and Neurodegenerative processes, currently working in Neurovirology. I also possess passion for BCI and signal encoding. Currently, I am investigating Covid19 associated neurodegeneration/neuropathies.
